	   <tr><td colspan=2>Things to do in these situations:<br><br>1) Take the hits<br>2) Have an enchanter<br>3) Charm the monster<br>4) Be crowd control yourself<br>5) Stop singing/attacking and hope another groupie agros him off you<br>6) Die<br><br>Bard songs are VERY taunting, especially heal and Selo's.  Try to avoid those in mid-combat, if you can.<br>&nbsp;<br>Ensis Arament</td></tr>
