<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97098582026771></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97098582026771><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=4&mid=97098582026771>RE: What can I do to survive in groups as a bard?</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Oct 8th 2:17 AM 2000</td>
