	   <tr><td colspan=2>Bards really have little control over this until they get the ability to mez (Pixy Strike) or Charm...<br><br>You can teach your group members to help keep you alive with the seperate and root method until you can control mobs yourself...<br><br>Other than that... have a good friend in a cleric that watches your health like a hawk...<br><br>Have fun... have a happy attitude about the deaths... sometimes you just cant avoid them... but when you hit the age of croud control... you are in your own hands then...<br><br>~Yorke Amusia<br>&lt;the Wicked&gt; Court Jester<br>Ambassador/Poet to &lt;Lore Keepers&gt;<br>Innoruuk's Happy Bard for 52 songs<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
