	   <tr><td colspan=2>This has happened to me many MANY times and my advice is this: Stand there, let the tank hit the mob a few times, and back off. 99 out of 100 times the mob will turn around and focus on the tank. It is usually a good idea to stop attacking the mob, but never EVER stop singing. If that doesnt work, god help you. Wash, Rinse, and Repeat. =)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
